{"kind":"article","abstract":[{"text":"iBooks Author lets you use a drag-and-drop interface to create rich and immersive books for the iBookstore. Discover best practices for book design and asset preparation, and learn how to use the iBooks Author interface efficiently to develop your book. See how to enhance your book with rich media such as audio, video, and animations, plus get tips for testing your book before submitting it to the iBookstore.","type":"text"}],"sampleCodeDownload":{"action":{"identifier":"https:\/\/nonstrict.eu\/wwdcindex\/wwdc2013\/605\/","isActive":true,"overridingTitle":"Open on WWDCIndex","type":"reference"},"kind":"sampleDownload"},"metadata":{"modules":[{"name":"WWDC Notes"}],"title":"What’s New in iBooks Author","roleHeading":"WWDC13","role":"sampleCode"},"primaryContentSections":[{"content":[{"text":"Overview","anchor":"overview","type":"heading","level":2},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"😱 “No Overview Available!”"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"Be the hero to change that by watching the video or reading the transcript on WWDCIndex and providing notes! It’s super easy:","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"isActive":true,"type":"reference","identifier":"https:\/\/wwdcnotes.com\/documentation\/wwdcnotes\/contributing"}],"type":"paragraph"}],"kind":"content"}],"sections":[],"variants":[{"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"swift"}],"paths":["\/documentation\/wwdcnotes\/wwdc13-605-whats-new-in-ibooks-author"]}],"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/WWDCNotes\/documentation\/WWDCNotes","doc:\/\/WWDCNotes\/documentation\/WWDCNotes\/WWDC13"]]},"schemaVersion":{"minor":3,"major":0,"patch":0},"identifier":{"interfaceLanguage":"swift","url":"doc:\/\/WWDCNotes\/documentation\/WWDCNotes\/WWDC13-605-Whats-New-in-iBooks-Author"},"references":{"https://nonstrict.eu/wwdcindex/wwdc2013/605/":{"checksum":null,"type":"download","identifier":"https:\/\/nonstrict.eu\/wwdcindex\/wwdc2013\/605\/","url":"https:\/\/nonstrict.eu\/wwdcinde